No. 09-11052. Floyd Junior Powell, Petitioner v. Tony A. Keller, et al. 561 U.S. 1022, 130 S. Ct. 3529,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1087,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5282. June 28, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for a writ of certiorari United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 367 Fed. Appx. 402.
